title: Fix broken build
message:
Fix broken build

- v7 appcompat requires v4 support
  https://developer.android.com/topic/libraries/support-library/features.html

- PhotoPickerFragment needed a field added for listPopupWindow

- Update Circle, Travis configs for new build tools
  - There are no tests, so no need to call connectedCheck

- Update Android Gradle Plugin to 2.1.2
